Welcome to the Map2Green App!

This app is intended to help support city planners to visualize and analyze spatial data for the purpose of improving sustainable transportation in the City of Vancouver. The Map2Green app has a layer that shows citizen accessibility to current sustainable transportation options including bike lanes, green (walking) routes, and public transit.
